OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,FUK hotel chains and holiday parks have
OL,7,Fwarned that a proposed surge in
OL,8,Fbusiness rates could impact employment
OL,9,Fand prices as they called for expected
OL,10,Fsupport for pubs to be extended across
OL,11,Fthe sector.
OL,13,FFirms including Hilton, Butlin's and
OL,14,FTravelodge are among more than 130
OL,15,Faccommodation businesses who have
OL,16,Fcalled on Chancellor Rachel Reeves for
OL,17,Fan urgent solution.
