OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,FIn November's autumn budget, the
OL,7,FChancellor launched significant
OL,8,Fchanges to business rates, the
OL,9,Fcommercial property tax impacting
OL,10,Fhospitality and high street firms.
OL,12,FThe Treasury announced a reduced
OL,13,Fmultiplier for calculating rates but
OL,14,Falso revealed that a current 40%
OL,15,Fdiscount for retail, hospitality and
OL,16,Fleisure firms will end in April.
OL,18,FThis will be replaced by significant
OL,19,Ftransition relief but this will phase
OL,20,Fout after three years.
