OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,FThe budget also confirmed that new
OL,7,Fproperty valuations will be used for
OL,8,F2026, which have contributed to
OL,9,Fsignificant long-term rate increases
OL,10,Ffor hotels, as well as other
OL,11,Fhospitality businesses.
OL,13,FThe average hotels business rates bill
OL,14,Fwill increase by 115% by April 2029,
OL,15,Ftotalling #205,200, according to
OL,16,Fanalysis of Valuation Office Agency
OL,17,Fdata by the UKHospitality trade group.
