OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,FIn a letter to Ms Reeves, the bosses
OL,7,Fsaid the increases are "not something
OL,8,Fbusinesses will be able to easily
OL,9,Fabsorb", and that passing costs on to
OL,10,Fguests would further add to cost-of-
OL,11,Fliving pressures.
OL,13,FThe Government has indicated that pubs
OL,14,Fare expected to receive additional
OL,15,Ffinancial support after recent
OL,16,Fwarnings from the sector due to their
OL,17,Fimpending business rates increases.
