OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,FHotel bosses have stressed that any
OL,7,Fsupport measures must be extended to
OL,8,Faccommodation providers and other
OL,9,Fhospitality operators.
OL,11,FIn the letter, they said: "While
OL,12,Fadditional support for the hospitality
OL,13,Fsector is welcome, it's critical that
OL,14,Fit should not only extend to pubs but
OL,15,Fshould be a whole-sector solution.
