OL,3,CHotel bosses call for financial
OL,4,Csupport as business rates set to surge
OL,6,F"These changes to business rates
OL,7,Fpresent the most significant challenge
OL,8,Fto accommodation providers in terms of
OL,9,Ftheir ongoing viability, and many will
OL,10,Fface tough decisions in terms of
OL,11,Femployment and their ability to invest.
OL,13,F"This issue will grow in severity over
OL,14,Fthe coming years, as transitional
OL,15,Frelief tapers off ` this is not
OL,16,Fsomething businesses will be able to
OL,17,Feasily absorb, while passing costs
OL,18,Fonto guests would further add to the
OL,19,Fcost-of-living pressures already
OL,20,Fgreatly affecting the British public."
