OL,6,FKate Nicholls, chairwoman of
OL,7,FUKHospitality, said: "Hotels and
OL,8,Fholiday parks are the hardest hit by
OL,9,Fbusiness rates hikes, facing 115%
OL,10,Fincreases.
OL,12,F"As this coalition so clearly sets out
OL,13,F` this will only have adverse impacts
OL,14,Fon employment, investment and, in some
OL,15,Fcases, business viability.
